nodes.text: The Tetan elite was a self-indulgent group of young aristocrats from the Empress Teta system that turned to the dark side around the year 3997 BBY. They dabbled in primitive magic as a mean of amusement, eventually tapping into the Force's dark side. The first of the group to fall was Satal Keto, who organized his cohorts into a secret group called the Krath.[source?]
